Description: Data exposed: 45 different domains- each with a separate data set. The data sets are focused on scientific research; these include DBLP- Citeseer- CORDIS- NSF- EPSRC- RAE2001- KISTI- UNLOCODE- Wordnet- voiD- OS- OAI.  Size of dump and data set: ~150 million triples.  The data is available as Linked Data- SPARQL endpoint and RDF dumps- and a simple browser is provided.  Semantic Web Sitemaps and voiD descriptions provided.  Index of the datasets is at http://www.rkbexplorer.com/data.  Dumps can be found by for example http://dotac.rkbexplorer.com/sitemap.xml.
Authors: Name: Hugh Glaser & Ian Millard; Email:hg@ecs.soton.ac.uk
Sources: Web:http://www.rkbexplorer.com/data Name:Hugh Glaser & Ian Millard Email:hg@ecs.soton.ac.uk
